{"tid":1461305,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"分析五毛彈弓打爆眼論","createTime":"2019-08-13T07:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:34:36.000Z","uid":259302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"438053c0b27e1b95332da504efdf0ebc771bef43","tid":1461305,"uid":259302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:10:02.000Z","msg":"其實個point唔係打唔打得爆塊鏡，因為彈弓係打得爆。3m 1621 衝擊規格係ansi z87.1，淨係防到1joule，官方條測試片都淨係試1joule鋼珠射落去。但我上網查，彈弓係輕易過10joules，甚至去到100joules都無問題，所以彈弓係打得爆個塊鏡。<br />\n<br />\n攻擊點1：布袋彈入面本身就係裝啲2mm嘅細鉛珠，而彈弓用嘅起碼10mm以上，除非有證據打入個粒係10mm或以上大嘅鐵珠除則證明唔到係彈弓打嘅。唔係就禁話有鐵珠就係彈弓打。<br />\n<br />\n攻擊點2：女義士係first aid，唔會企得前過前線，何來打警察個陣誤中女義士？係人群度拉恒彈弓一早比人禁低左啦。<br />\n<br />\n攻擊點3：DLLM根本有相有直播見到布袋彈卡係個眼罩度<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AB%8B%E5%BB%A3%E5%82%B3-%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E8%AD%89%E7%88%86%E7%9C%BC%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%9C%BC%E7%BD%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%83%E8%A2%8B%E5%BD%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%259C%25BC%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%25A2%258B%25E5%25BD%2588%2F&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb21VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=be6d7a5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%259C%25BC%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%25A2%258B%25E5%25BD%2588%2F&h=2043aca2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AB%8B%E5%BB%A3%E5%82%B3-%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E8%AD%89%E7%88%86%E7%9C%BC%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%9C%BC%E7%BD%A9%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%83%E8%A2%8B%E5%BD%88/</a><br />\n<br />\n攻擊點3.1：今朝離撚晒譜，見到有人on9度話布袋彈係用彈弓打嘅。首先，射出黎個舊布袋彈係自制到，而且唔難，但成本高兼費時。你前線用彈弓都係想打傷警犬姐，會唔會禁麻煩走去整布袋彈啊？打落警犬度布袋彈又卸力，直接買一袋直徑10～20mm嘅鐵珠用啦！"},{"pid":"3a84b59881abfbea8f072b0516cac90f27dc3dcc","tid":1461305,"uid":259302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:10:39.000Z","msg":"歡迎補充，用作對付蠢人嘅彈藥"},{"pid":"00d50bf9440a8276af6e834f5b5371d7a128d2b4","tid":1461305,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n【推出去】對付五毛好方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1461318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1461318</a>"},{"pid":"ed9a087d5d433e5bf540adca34203e711751af70","tid":1461305,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"3 已經夠"},{"pid":"e805357e12b07b993a2dc32560179dd87304dc8b","tid":1461305,"uid":139677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:09:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c108da068cd02285b8fe1d5c9e47d49107898daf","tid":1461305,"uid":259302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed9a087d5d433e5bf540adca34203e711751af70","tid":1461305,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"3 已經夠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:34:36.000Z","msg":"五毛係無所不其極，望下3.1就知，而且我嘅重點唔係對付五毛，係個啲睇下留言嘅蠢人"}]}